# Support

Welcome to the Databrary support site.

We've gathered information here to help you make better use of the site.

You'll find a comprehensive User Guide, a guide specifically for Institutions, a set of template documents, and information about Databrary's policies.

Throughout this site, we use special sections to indicate tips,

cautionary notes,

warnings,
